<FIRST>r a PM-Nielsens     06-21 0474</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Nielsens,0486</SECOND>
<HEAD>A Year at the Top for NBC</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KATHRYN BAKER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Television Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
