ble to stand up and take the law into their own hands,'' he said. Legislators joined in condemning the violence. <PERSON> Eitan </PERSON> said the incidents `` must shock us all into seeing what can happen in the future.'' <PERSON> Sarid </PERSON> said: `` All is ready for a civil war. There are enough weapons to prove people are ready to kill innocent civilians.''
