ll management when to cook more and when to discard food that is past its prime. For customers, the computerization will cut time spent in line about 3 percent and make it easier to change orders, said the company, a division of <ORGANIZATION> Pepsico </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc </ORGANIZATION>.
